overview: Kizuna AI's 5th Anniversary Birthday Live "Kizuna AI 5th Birthday Live "A.I.Party 2021" will be held at Zepp Haneda!  To have the audience enjoy a sense of unity and live performance that only an actual venue can provide, Kizuna AI has teamed up with a real live band for her first time!  This will surely become a special event suitable for her 5th anniversary!
title: Kizuna AI 5th Birthday Live "A.I.Party 2021"
